{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Push notifications keep users up-to-date when their apps have data waiting for them on remote servers. Local notifications let apps generate notifications locally, without relying on a remote server. Learn best practices for creating notifications that get a user’s attention through any combination of an alert message, a distinctive sound, or number badging of the application—even when your app isn’t running."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/129\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-129-Implementing-Local-and-Push-Notifications"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-129-implementing-local-and-push-notifications"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC10","title":"Implementing Local and Push Notifications"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC10":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","title":"WWDC10","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10","